  <brief_title>Randomized Trial to Assess the Impact of a Screening Program on Upper Aerodigestive Tract Cancer Mortality in a High Risk Population</brief_title>
  <official_title>DEPISTORL - THANCS (Trial of Head And Neck Cancer Screening) Randomized Multicenter Trial to Assess the Impact of a Screening Program for Heavy Alcohol Drinkers and Smokers Treated in Alcohol Addiction Clinics on Upper Aerodigestive Tract Cancer Mortality.</official_title>
